Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~~哈哈哈哈哈~~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.71,0:00:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憎 伊奧利亞·舒恩伯格的亡靈們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人 亞歷桑德羅·科納
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將超度你們去新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia 剎那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始驅逐目標
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.97,0:00:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 瞄準集裝箱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順利的話至少能炸了那對鉗子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:00:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.69,0:00:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 毫髮無傷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.44,0:01:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點本事就像挑戰Alvatore
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑掉大牙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.45,0:01:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲爾德 Meister們情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nadleeh重傷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.83,0:01:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞…沒有應答
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.95,0:01:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios 機體損傷嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與敵方兩台MS交戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.11,0:01:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶翼機躲在衛星附近某處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.19,0:01:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種機體狀況逃不了多遠的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太失敗了 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.34,0:01:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.29,0:01:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊去 阿勒路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.75,0:01:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生死一線間都無所作為的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.14,0:01:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.11,0:01:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕吸人鮮血
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.53,0:01:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.69,0:01:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.81,0:01:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有聽到世界的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括這次戰鬥的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,額 終於有幹勁了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓那女人瞧瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何謂真正的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.16,0:02:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「超兵」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接命中線路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配合軸線
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出腳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並同時攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.72,0:02:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架機體為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.59,0:02:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此一時彼一時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 阿勒路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那武器是和Throne相同的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 合體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.95,0:03:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN-Armor什麼的…又能如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fang
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Field展開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝上去 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.02,0:04:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死不悔改
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.61,0:04:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下地獄去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:04:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.54,0:05:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不可能  區區一台Gundam就把我的Alvatore…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.65,0:06:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 我明明是完美的超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.18,0:06:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不明白呢 女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.35,0:06:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.23,0:06:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是什麼完美的超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然腦量子波帶來了超快的反應能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你的思維速度卻沒能跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是像動物一樣靠本能行動而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情…才沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你的行動才會被看穿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反應與思維的融合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是超兵的經典形態
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.48,0:06:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這光芒是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個系統嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了 女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.23,0:07:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在 比利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校 中校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼 別管我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續戰鬥 少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.43,0:07:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校不在的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又會孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪…瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞 回答 拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.59,0:08:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是擁有原版太陽爐的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半吊子機師也能讓我如此頭痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.51,0:08:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你嗎 歪曲伊奧利亞·舒恩伯格計劃的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過主角變成了我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 主角就是我 亞歷桑德羅·科納
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:09:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞與再生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界在「天人」的武力介入下瓦解 為實現大一統而重新再生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 我將以我的方式 重建這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要的是支配嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是正確引導才對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那個新世界 容不下你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉身碎骨吧 Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扼腕痛惜吧 伊奧利亞·舒恩伯格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:10:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,統合世界 將人類帶向新時代的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我這個活在當代的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.74,0:10:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞的系統嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.79,0:10:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了世界的扭曲點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 你就是其元兇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再生已經開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.51,0:10:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你仍執迷於破壞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 知道為何Exia裝備有實體劍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.11,0:10:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了對抗GN Field
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃中有對Gundam進行戰鬥的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關鍵時刻 你將是我們最後的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給你了 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一個只能選擇戰鬥的破壞者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要戰鬥 為擊敗催生戰爭的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉碎這個世界扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用武力來根除戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是「天人」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Field被…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam將成就它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利馮茲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞歷桑德羅·科納
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是位出色的配角
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這並非伊奧利亞·舒恩伯格的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是成為了我的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利馮茲 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被統合的世界就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 你竟利用了科納一族的夙願…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說 怪小氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利馮茲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.31,0:12:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flag 擬太陽爐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想你 想死我了 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:12:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光束刀？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為哈瓦德和達利爾 討還血債
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這台GN Flag
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有通信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是當時的少年？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我與你的邂逅是命中注定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 充滿戰鬥的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為你壓倒性的性能意亂情迷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺 正是所謂的愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一旦超越了愛 便因愛生恨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好比過於強烈的信仰會誘發內戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然明白 為何還戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問軍人為何而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被扭曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜你所賜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我必須擊倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界如何無關緊要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是 世界的一部分嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這就是世界的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯了 你只不過是執迷於貫徹自我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這顆扭曲的心 由我來斬斷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.85,0:14:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得好啊 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈瓦德 達利爾 血債…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒劇終
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃仍在進行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少把太陽爐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Drive從Nadleeh上…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算能安心上路 來找你了 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.19,0:16:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索瑪·比利斯…怎麼會  是瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早就知道？ 哈雷路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道的話 你就無法再戰鬥了 等死而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 結局都一樣 我先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷路亞 難道…怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉娜·伊斯邁爾 當你讀到這封信時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.38,0:16:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不在這世上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「以武力來根除戰爭」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天人」給了我戰鬥的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.48,0:16:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好比當時的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.98,0:17:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.09,0:17:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何 世界如此扭曲著 這扭曲又來自何方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何 人總會在無意識間產生惡意 為何 從不試圖反省這份惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何 會有人肆意踐踏他人的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何 人類支配和被支配
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何互相傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻又為何 拚死掙扎求生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 一直追尋著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為與你相見 就能獲得答案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在另一條道路上 和我有著同樣的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定能找到人與人之間互相理解的道路 找到我的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:17:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.09,0:18:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直追尋著 與Gundam一同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.84,0:18:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與Gundam…一同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲 好久沒發郵件給你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.63,0:18:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩年沒有收到你的回音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.65,0:18:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我有件事非說不可
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從今年開始將在宇宙工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.10,0:18:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有過許多傷心事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我這一小小的夢想成為現實
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以希望幫我實現另一個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等著你 路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天上等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.08,0:19:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是GN粒子的光芒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.54,0:19:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪裏的機體？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是聯邦的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.19,0:19:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子的顏色不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.95,0:19:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那光芒…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.48,0:19:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 那光芒是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.12,0:19:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合國改名為地球聯邦後一年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們獲得聯邦全部328個成員國的贊同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解散各國軍隊 實現一元化 在此宣佈組建地球聯邦維和軍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有國家的軍隊都成為過去 我們維和軍成為世界唯一軍事組織時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:20:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的世界統一方得以成就
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為先驅者 我們將全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣世界算是改變了吧 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢 現在的世界合您口味嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人期待呢 世界的繼續改變
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的未來從此開始 「變革者」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅途辛苦了 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:20:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一台剛下線
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正進行實戰性檢測
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它的機體呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.19,0:21:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按預定即將下線
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意我參觀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一代的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.65,0:21:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是0 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首台成功搭載太陽爐的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽爐已經卸下 裝載在機體上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.85,0:21:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可用上它也不匹配
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.67,0:21:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使用Exia的太陽爐 也不能保證順利運轉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變世界的機體  00 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷路亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:40.55,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}ねえ　こんな形の出逢いしか　なかったの？　悲しいね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:52.85,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}あなたに　死んでも殺めて　欲しくも無い　お願い
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:20:04.62,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}運命さえ飲み込まれ　沈みそうな　海へと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:14.81,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}願いよ風に乗って　夜明けの鐘を鳴らせよ　鳥のように
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:17.58,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}my wishes over their airspace
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.58,0:20:27.09,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}無数の波を超え　明日へ立ち向かうあなたを　守りたまえ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.09,0:20:29.79,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}my life I trade in for your pain
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:35.24,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}振り向かず羽ばたけ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:42.33,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}この想いを運んで　あの空を飛んでく
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:49.44,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}未来は誰にも　撃ち落とせない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:40.55,Lastcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}吶 除了這樣的相見 別無他法麼? 悲傷 徹骨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:52.85,Lastcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}你 即使我墮入地獄 也不願傷害 希望 絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:20:04.62,Lastcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}命運也被點點啃噬 墮向那絕望的深海
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:14.81,Lastcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}願望啊願望請乘上疾風 去敲響破曉的鍾 如飛鳥一般
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.58,0:20:27.09,Lastcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}超越吧超越那無數風浪 向明日抗爭的你 請替我守護
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:35.24,Lastcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}莫再回首 振翅去飛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:42.33,Lastcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}請帶著請帶著這份思念 飛到那一片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:49.44,Lastcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}那是誰都不能擊落的未來

